     "Single-onset. METAL-CRASH & DEBRIS is the same timbre with a multi-onset cluster (transient_count >= 3, high onset_rate_per_second); that onset count is the whole boundary.",
     "The object survives: no dense HF fracture burst or debris tail as in METAL-BREAK.",
